description: "This mid-18th century map features labels noting the local populations, including the Kemois of the mountains and deserts of Cochinchinae (Vietnam) and the Byayos of Borneo. The map’s cartouche is embellished with maritime and military paraphernalia."
title: "Carte   des   Indes   Orientalis   one   feuille   ...   les   Indes   deca   la   Riviere   de   Ganges,   le   Golfe   de   Bengale,   Siam,   Malacca,   Sumatra   "
